dc_title_s: Hydrography (Polygon and Line)  Sawyer County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Sawyer County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Sawyer_Hydro_2014.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Sawyer_HydroLine_2014', and 'Sawyer_HydroPoly_2014'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
